==English==

===Etymology===
First attested in [[w:1545|1545]], from [[Latin]] [[extantem]], from [[extare]], from [[ex-]] ''out'' + [[stare]] ''stand'', from [[PIE]] [[*sta-]] ''to stand''.

===Pronunciation===
{{audio|en-us-extant.ogg|Audio (US)}}
[[IPA]]: /ˈɛkstənt/ /ɛkˈstænt/
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ænt|-ænt]]

===Adjective===
{{en-adj-more}}

# Still in [[existence]].
# Currently [[existing]]; not having [[disappeared]].
# Still [[alive]]; not [[extinct]].

